---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - AI Website Builders">

  <!-- BRUTALIST HERO - Coupon site style -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-[#FFF8F0]">
    <!-- Geometric accent -->
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[45%] h-full opacity-[0.04]" style="background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, #F5521A 0px, #F5521A 1px, transparent 1px, transparent 12px);"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-32 h-32 bg-[#F5521A]/5 rounded-tr-[100px]"></div>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 max-w-7xl relative">
      <div class="py-12 md:py-16 lg:py-20">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-6">

          <!-- Brutalist badge -->
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-3 bg-white border-[3px] border-[#F5521A] shadow-[0_4px_0_0_rgba(245,82,26,0.3)]">
            <div class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-[#F5521A] rotate-45"></span>
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-[#F5521A] rotate-45" style="animation-delay: 0.15s"></span>
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-[#F5521A] rotate-45" style="animation-delay: 0.3s"></span>
            </div>
            <span class="text-xs font-black tracking-widest text-gray-800" style="font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;">
              INDEPENDENT TESTING • NO FLUFF
            </span>
          </div>

          <!-- MASSIVE headline -->
          <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-black leading-[0.9] tracking-tight text-gray-900">
            <span class="block">I got tired of</span>
            <span class="block text-[#F5521A] mt-2">fake AI tool reviews</span>
          </h1>

          <!-- Personal subheadline -->
          <div class="max-w-2xl">
            <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-800/95 font-medium leading-relaxed">
              So I started building real websites with these tools and documenting what actually happens. Not the marketing fluff—the real experience.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

	<!-- Story - brutalist style -->
	<section class="py-16 px-6 bg-white">
		<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
			<h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-8 flex items-center gap-3">
        <div class="w-1 h-8 bg-[#F5521A]"></div>
        How this started
      </h2>
			<div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-600">
				<p class="mb-4">
					In 2024, I was looking for an AI website builder for a side project. I read probably 20 "reviews"—all of them
					listed the same 5 tools, all with 4.5+ star ratings, all with affiliate links.
				</p>
				<p class="mb-4">
					So I tried the top recommendation. It was awful. The export didn't work. The AI content was hallucinating features.
					The "free" plan was basically unusable.
				</p>
				<p class="mb-4">
					I tried the second recommendation. Same story. The third, the fourth—they all had issues that none of the reviews mentioned.
				</p>
				<p class="mb-4">
					That's when I realized: <strong class="text-gray-900">these weren't reviews at all. They were SEO-optimized affiliate bait.</strong>
				</p>
				<p>
					So I started doing my own testing. Properly. Spending actual time with each tool. Building real sites.
					Documenting the problems. Sharing screenshots of the bugs.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- What makes us different - brutalist cards -->
	<section class="py-16 px-6 bg-gray-50">
		<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
			<h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-8 flex items-center gap-3">
        <div class="w-1 h-8 bg-[#F5521A]"></div>
        What I do differently
      </h2>
			<div class="space-y-6">
				<div class="bg-white p-6 border-[3px] border-[#F5521A]/20 relative overflow-hidden hover:border-[#F5521A]/50 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-[#F5521A] text-white flex items-center justify-center font-black text-xl">1</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-black text-gray-900 text-lg mb-2">I spend 10-50 hours per tool</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Not a 30-minute demo. I build actual complete websites from scratch.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
				<div class="bg-white p-6 border-2 border-dashed border-gray-300 hover:border-[#F5521A]/50 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-gray-900 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-black text-xl">2</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-black text-gray-900 text-lg mb-2">I document the problems</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Loading issues, bugs, confusing UX, hidden limitations—I tell you about all of it.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
				<div class="bg-gray-900 p-6 border-[3px] border-transparent hover:border-[#F5521A]/30 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-[#F5521A] text-white flex items-center justify-center font-black text-xl">3</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-black text-white text-lg mb-2">Affiliate links are disclosed</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400">I use affiliate links, but I'll still tell you if a tool sucks. Commissions don't buy my opinion.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
				<div class="bg-[#F5521A] p-6 border-[3px] border-[#D44A1A] shadow-[0_4px_0_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.2)] hover:shadow-[0_6px_0_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.25)] hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-white text-[#F5521A] flex items-center justify-center font-black text-xl">4</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-black text-white text-lg mb-2">I re-test regularly</h3>
              <p class="text-white/80">Tools change. I update reviews to reflect current reality, not what was true 6 months ago.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Brutalist CTA -->
	<section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-[#F5521A] relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.03]" style="background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, #000 0px, #000 1px, transparent 1px, transparent 12px);"></div>
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 max-w-4xl relative">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-white leading-tight mb-6">
          Questions? Feedback?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-white/90 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Think I missed something? Want to suggest a tool for me to test?
        </p>
        <a
          href="mailto:hello@aiwebsitebuilders.com"
          class="inline-block px-8 py-4 bg-white text-[#F5521A] font-black text-lg uppercase tracking-wider border-[3px] border-white shadow-[0_6px_0_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.2)] hover:shadow-[0_8px_0_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.25)] hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-300"
         
        >
          Get in touch
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>